      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/7010248.Jas_T_Ward">About Jas T. Ward</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/7010248.Jas_T_Ward"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1587074235p3/7010248.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/7010248.Jas_T_Ward">Jas T. Ward
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
469
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer6139914323980666830">About the Author<br/><br/>Born and raised in Texas, Ward is a mixed bag of creativity spinning tales of paranormal, urban fantasy and even dark romance and horror; wrapped within a love story. <br/><br/>She’s been dared by her readers to write a few contemporary romances but even those reads have characters that are real and twisted by their creator. It did, however, spawn her romance tag line: Romance - The Ward Way</span>
  <span id="freeText6139914323980666830" style="display:none">About the Author<br /><br />Born and raised in Texas, Ward is a mixed bag of creativity spinning tales of paranormal, urban fantasy and even dark romance and horror; wrapped within a love story. <br /><br />She’s been dared by her readers to write a few contemporary romances but even those reads have characters that are real and twisted by their creator. It did, however, spawn her romance tag line: Romance - The Ward Way. <br /><br />Mother of three diverse and independent bold children, Ward prides herself for being the “Queen Niche’ Bitch” which is a handy way of saying she sucks writing to market. <br />But her readers don’t seem to mind.<br /><br />Ward can be contacted via:<br />Facebook: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.facebook.com/AuthorJasTWard">www.facebook.com/AuthorJasTWard</a><br />Website: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://authorjastward.com">http://authorjastward.com</a><br />Email: Hello@authorjastward.com<br /></span>
